# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: akses_role

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `akses_role`;

CREATE TABLE `akses_role` (
  `akses_role` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `id_menu` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `id_role` int(11) NOT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`akses_role`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=126 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: backup
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `backup`;

CREATE TABLE `backup` (
  `id_backup` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `tgl` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT current_timestamp() ON UPDATE current_timestamp(),
  `file` varchar(128) NOT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id_backup`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=20 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4;

INSERT INTO `backup` (`id_backup`, `tgl`, `file`) VALUES (19, '2020-08-13 19:05:37', 'db-backup-on-2020-08-13-19-05-37');


#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: barang
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `barang`;

CREATE TABLE `barang` (
  `id_barang` char(7) NOT NULL,
  `id_kategori` char(7) DEFAULT NULL,
  `id_supplier` char(7) DEFAULT NULL,
  `satuan` varchar(12) DEFAULT NULL,
  `barcode` varchar(128) DEFAULT NULL,
  `nama_barang` varchar(128) DEFAULT NULL,
  `nama_pendek` varchar(128) DEFAULT NULL,
  `harga_pokok` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `harga_jual` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `potongan_member` int(11) DEFAULT 0,
  `profit` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `profit_member` int(11) DEFAULT 0,
  `stok` float DEFAULT 0,
  `diskon` int(11) DEFAULT 0,
  `gambar` varchar(128) DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id_barang`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: detail_pembelian
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `detail_pembelian`;

CREATE TABLE `detail_pembelian` (
  `id_detail_pembelian` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `faktur_pembelian` varchar(10) NOT NULL,
  `id_barang` char(7) NOT NULL,
  `jumlah` float NOT NULL,
  `total_harga` int(11) NOT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id_detail_pembelian`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: detail_pengembalian
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `detail_pengembalian`;

CREATE TABLE `detail_pengembalian` (
  `faktur_pengembalian` varchar(128) NOT NULL,
  `id_barang` char(7) NOT NULL,
  `jumlah` float NOT NULL,
  `total_harga` int(11) NOT NULL
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: detail_penjualan
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `detail_penjualan`;

CREATE TABLE `detail_penjualan` (
  `faktur_penjualan` varchar(128) NOT NULL,
  `id_barang` char(7) NOT NULL,
  `jumlah` float NOT NULL,
  `total_harga` int(11) NOT NULL
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: detail_stok
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `detail_stok`;

CREATE TABLE `detail_stok` (
  `id_stok` char(7) NOT NULL,
  `id_barang` char(7) NOT NULL,
  `jumlah` float NOT NULL
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: detail_stok_opname
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `detail_stok_opname`;

CREATE TABLE `detail_stok_opname` (
  `id_detail_stok_opname` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `id_stok_opname` char(7) NOT NULL,
  `id_barang` char(7) NOT NULL,
  `stok_komputer` float NOT NULL,
  `stok_fisik` float NOT NULL,
  `selisih` float NOT NULL,
  `kerugian` int(11) NOT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id_detail_stok_opname`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: karyawan
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `karyawan`;

CREATE TABLE `karyawan` (
  `id_karyawan` char(7) NOT NULL,
  `id_outlet` char(7) NOT NULL,
  `nama_karyawan` varchar(128) NOT NULL,
  `alamat` varchar(128) NOT NULL,
  `jk` enum('L','P') NOT NULL,
  `telepon` char(12) NOT NULL,
  `email` varchar(30) NOT NULL,
  `jabatan` varchar(128) NOT NULL,
  `gambar` varchar(128) NOT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id_karyawan`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: kategori
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `kategori`;

CREATE TABLE `kategori` (
  `id_kategori` char(7) NOT NULL,
  `nama_kategori` varchar(30) NOT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id_kategori`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4;

INSERT INTO `kategori` (`id_kategori`, `nama_kategori`) VALUES ('KTR0001', 'Alat Tulis Kantor');
INSERT INTO `kategori` (`id_kategori`, `nama_kategori`) VALUES ('KTR0002', 'Kompoter');


#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: menu
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `menu`;

CREATE TABLE `menu` (
  `id_menu` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `nama_menu` varchar(255) NOT NULL,
  `icon` varchar(255) NOT NULL,
  `ada_submenu` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `submenu` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `url` varchar(255) NOT NULL,
  `urutan` int(11) NOT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id_menu`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=41 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: outlet
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `outlet`;

CREATE TABLE `outlet` (
  `id_outlet` char(7) NOT NULL,
  `nama_outlet` varchar(30) NOT NULL,
  `alamat` varchar(128) NOT NULL,
  `telepon` char(12) NOT NULL,
  `email` varchar(128) NOT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id_outlet`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4;

INSERT INTO `outlet` (`id_outlet`, `nama_outlet`, `alamat`, `telepon`, `email`) VALUES ('OTL0001', 'Ciwiey Jaya', 'Jl. Ciwidey\r\n', '083822623170', 'ciwideyjaya@gmail.com');

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: pelanggan
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `pelanggan`;

CREATE TABLE `pelanggan` (
  `id_pelanggan` char(7) NOT NULL,
  `nama_pelanggan` varchar(30) NOT NULL,
  `alamat` varchar(128) NOT NULL,
  `telepon` char(12) NOT NULL,
  `jk` enum('L','P') NOT NULL,
  `jenis` enum('umum','member') NOT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id_pelanggan`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4;

INSERT INTO `pelanggan` (`id_pelanggan`, `nama_pelanggan`, `alamat`, `telepon`, `jk`, `jenis`) VALUES ('PLG0001', 'Walk-in Client', 'Kp. Bojonggadog', '083822623170', 'L', 'umum');

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: pembayaran
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `pembayaran`;

CREATE TABLE `pembayaran` (
  `id_pembayaran` varchar(128) NOT NULL,
  `faktur_penjualan` varchar(128) NOT NULL,
  `tgl` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT current_timestamp(),
  `dibayar_dengan` varchar(128) NOT NULL,
  `nominal` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `no_kredit` varchar(128) NOT NULL,
  `no_debit` varchar(128) NOT NULL,
  `lampiran` varchar(128) NOT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id_pembayaran`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: pembayaran_pembelian
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `pembayaran_pembelian`;

CREATE TABLE `pembayaran_pembelian` (
  `id_pembayaran` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `faktur_pembelian` varchar(11) NOT NULL,
  `tgl` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT current_timestamp(),
  `dibayar_dengan` varchar(128) NOT NULL,
  `nominal` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `no_kredit` varchar(128) NOT NULL,
  `no_debit` varchar(128) NOT NULL,
  `lampiran` varchar(128) NOT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id_pembayaran`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: pembelian
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `pembelian`;

CREATE TABLE `pembelian` (
  `faktur_pembelian` varchar(10) NOT NULL,
  `id_supplier` char(7) NOT NULL,
  `id_petugas` char(7) NOT NULL,
  `tgl` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT current_timestamp(),
  `tgl_jatuh_tempo` date NOT NULL,
  `total_bayar` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `status` varchar(128) NOT NULL,
  `tgl_pembelian` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT '0000-00-00 00:00:00',
  `referensi` varchar(128) NOT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`faktur_pembelian`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: pengaturan
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `pengaturan`;

CREATE TABLE `pengaturan` (
  `id_pengaturan` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `logo` varchar(128) NOT NULL,
  `keterangan_invoice` varchar(225) NOT NULL,
  `diskon_member` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `potongan_member` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `nama_printer` varchar(128) NOT NULL,
  `print_otomatis` tinyint(4) NOT NULL,
  `smtp_host` varchar(128) NOT NULL,
  `smtp_email` varchar(128) NOT NULL,
  `smtp_username` varchar(128) NOT NULL,
  `smtp_password` varchar(128) NOT NULL,
  `smtp_port` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `peringatan_stok` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `hapus_riwayat_penjualan_otomatis` tinyint(4) NOT NULL,
  `lama_hari_penjualan` varchar(11) NOT NULL,
  `sesuaikan_hari_penjualan` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `hapus_riwayat_pembelian_otomatis` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `lama_hari_pembelian` varchar(11) NOT NULL,
  `sesuaikan_hari_pembelian` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `url_server` varchar(128) NOT NULL,
  `multi_outlet` tinyint(4) NOT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id_pengaturan`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=2 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: pengembalian
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `pengembalian`;

CREATE TABLE `pengembalian` (
  `faktur_pengembalian` varchar(128) NOT NULL,
  `faktur_penjualan` varchar(10) DEFAULT NULL,
  `id_pelanggan` char(7) NOT NULL,
  `id_petugas` char(7) NOT NULL,
  `id_outlet` char(7) NOT NULL,
  `tgl` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT current_timestamp(),
  `total_bayar` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `alasan` varchar(225) NOT NULL,
  `keterangan` text NOT NULL,
  `status` varchar(128) NOT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`faktur_pengembalian`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: penjualan
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `penjualan`;

CREATE TABLE `penjualan` (
  `faktur_penjualan` varchar(128) NOT NULL,
  `tgl` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT current_timestamp(),
  `tgl_jatuh_tempo` date NOT NULL DEFAULT '0000-00-00',
  `id_petugas` char(7) NOT NULL,
  `id_pelanggan` char(7) NOT NULL,
  `id_outlet` char(7) DEFAULT NULL,
  `total_bayar` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `diskon` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `potongan` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `status` varchar(128) NOT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`faktur_penjualan`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: petugas
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `petugas`;

CREATE TABLE `petugas` (
  `id_petugas` char(7) NOT NULL,
  `id_outlet` char(7) DEFAULT NULL,
  `nama_petugas` varchar(128) NOT NULL,
  `alamat` varchar(128) NOT NULL,
  `jk` enum('L','P') NOT NULL,
  `telepon` char(12) NOT NULL,
  `email` varchar(30) NOT NULL,
  `password` varchar(128) NOT NULL,
  `gambar` varchar(128) NOT NULL,
  `id_role` int(11) NOT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id_petugas`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: register
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `register`;

CREATE TABLE `register` (
  `id_register` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `id_petugas` char(7) NOT NULL,
  `id_outlet` char(7) DEFAULT NULL,
  `uang_awal` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `total_uang` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `mulai` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT current_timestamp(),
  `berakhir` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT '0000-00-00 00:00:00',
  `status` enum('open','close') NOT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id_register`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: role
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `role`;

CREATE TABLE `role` (
  `id_role` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `nama_role` varchar(30) NOT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id_role`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=6 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4;

INSERT INTO `role` (`id_role`, `nama_role`) VALUES (1, 'Admin');
INSERT INTO `role` (`id_role`, `nama_role`) VALUES (2, 'Kasir');


#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: satuan
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `satuan`;

CREATE TABLE `satuan` (
  `id_satuan` char(7) NOT NULL,
  `nama_satuan` varchar(30) NOT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id_satuan`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: stok
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `stok`;

CREATE TABLE `stok` (
  `id_stok` char(7) NOT NULL,
  `id_petugas` char(7) NOT NULL,
  `id_outlet` char(7) NOT NULL,
  `tgl` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT current_timestamp() ON UPDATE current_timestamp(),
  `keterangan` text NOT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id_stok`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: stok_opname
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `stok_opname`;

CREATE TABLE `stok_opname` (
  `id_stok_opname` char(7) NOT NULL,
  `tgl` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT current_timestamp(),
  `id_outlet` char(7) NOT NULL,
  `id_petugas` char(7) NOT NULL,
  `keterangan` text NOT NULL,
  `total_kerugian` int(11) NOT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id_stok_opname`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: stok_outlet
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `stok_outlet`;

CREATE TABLE `stok_outlet` (
  `id_stok_outlet` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `id_outlet` char(7) NOT NULL,
  `id_barang` char(7) NOT NULL,
  `stok` float NOT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id_stok_outlet`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: supplier
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `supplier`;

CREATE TABLE `supplier` (
  `id_supplier` char(7) NOT NULL,
  `nama_supplier` varchar(30) NOT NULL,
  `alamat` varchar(128) NOT NULL,
  `telepon` char(12) NOT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id_supplier`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4;

INSERT INTO `supplier` (`id_supplier`, `nama_supplier`, `alamat`, `telepon`) VALUES ('SPL0001', 'ALL', 'Bandung', '');


#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: token_petugas
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `token_petugas`;

CREATE TABLE `token_petugas` (
  `id_token_petugas` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `id_petugas` char(7) NOT NULL,
  `tgl` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT current_timestamp(),
  `token` varchar(128) NOT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id_token_petugas`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4;
